===================================
CiviMobile Extension
===================================

Mobile friendly interface for the specific actions in CiviCRM

Features include:

* Contacts
- Search Contacts
- Add/Update/View Contacts
- Proximity search for contacts

* Events
- participant search and checkin

* Survey
- Search for suvery
- Record survey responses

Requirement: CiviCRM v4.7.x

Using CiviMobile
- Install the extension
- CiviMobile menu item will be automatically added to the CiviCRM navigation menu
- Clicking on the CiviMobile menu, it will switch you to CiviMobile interface

You can directly access the CiviMobile interface on your moblile using <sitename>/civicrm/mobile/login

Note: This extension does not convert web interface of CiviCRM to mobile friendly. 

